title: [Primates]
description: Long vines crisscross throughout the habitat to the south and dense foliage provide ample coverage for the creatures that lurk within.  Beams of sunlight filter through the thick canopy, highlighting the grassy floor.  A white furred uakari can be seen amongst the bushes on the ground, while a bright yellow baboon sits high in a tree.
